rce src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367640/extras/ef71a06050c2989cd32b780c56e6b955.webm?t=1762785592\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367640/extras/ef71a06050c2989cd32b780c56e6b955.mp4?t=1762785592\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Strengthen your hero by upgrading your skills, choosing between the sword or magic. As you progress through the game, gather valuable experience points to unlock new talents and enhance your character's prowess. Train diligently and develop a versatile skillset, ensuring you're well-equipped for the epic confrontation with the fearsome archmonsters that await.<br><br>With relentless monsters at every turn, stay vigilant and survive as long as possible on the desolate battlefields.",
